						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://blog.xkcd.com/2012/03/22/im-visiting-cnu-on-april-4th/" title="12:48 pm" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2012-03-22T12:48:36+00:00" pubdate>March 22, 2012</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://blog.xkcd.com/author/xkcd/" title="View all posts by xkcd" rel="author">xkcd</a></span></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
